IInstance
           Instances are the "objects" in the knowledge base.
IInstanceImplementation
          The implementation of an instance, generated and initialized by a ConceptManager after a knowledge model has been read.
IKnowledge
          IKnowledge defines the methods that are common to both IConcepts and IInstances.
IKnowledgeSubject
          Extends IKnowledge to define "subjects", meaning first-class objects that have a right to exist independently in a knowledge space.
